{"tid":2489775,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬隊巴被利物浦球迷襲擊","createTime":"2021-04-15T07:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:38:23.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6079f61a21b3c15c65b7d9fde85c9505059231cb","tid":2489775,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"周四(15日)凌晨歐聯8強次回合，皇馬隊巴前往晏菲路球場途中，遭利物浦球迷掟石襲擊，導致1個車窗玻璃破碎，幸好冇人受傷，但事件已引起當局關注，呢班足球流氓隨時連累利物浦被歐洲足協處罰。<br />\n<br />\n根據西班牙《馬卡報》爆料，當時<strong><span class=\"red\">皇馬職球員乘坐隊巴前往球場，喺晏菲路球場附近，遭人掟石襲擊，車窗破碎出現一大塊破損，好彩冇造成傷亡。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n事發後利物浦發言人譴責有關行為可恥，並向皇馬道歉，紅軍亦會配合英國警方調查，捉拿施襲者。由於今場屬於利物浦主場賽事，事件可能會連累紅軍被歐洲足協處罰，球隊最後仲出局，可以話係雙失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/odNm7qei_4Qj64EElaGhzQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/zP0fgcipO.M4yt559Uoy2g--~B/aD0yMjY4O3c9NDAzMjthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/pa-sport.com/f7f34a71617a6a8f1c67d21b11e9b1bd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FodNm7qei_4Qj64EElaGhzQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzP0fgcipO.M4yt559Uoy2g--~B%2FaD0yMjY4O3c9NDAzMjthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fpa-sport.com%2Ff7f34a71617a6a8f1c67d21b11e9b1bd&h=5c810915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-prod.liverpoolecho.co.uk/incoming/article20388742.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/0_WhatsApp-Image-2021-04-14-at-194834jpeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.liverpoolecho.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle20388742.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2F0_WhatsApp-Image-2021-04-14-at-194834jpeg.jpg&h=4148f499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28d5aab699a247457811681a8453742b80b310f5","tid":2489775,"uid":27287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6079f61a21b3c15c65b7d9fde85c9505059231cb","tid":2489775,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT